raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
set PhoneUnlocks.leak = \"sorgroup1\"
Mabel: Hey babe!
Mabel: img: mabel/95
Mabel: How did your uhm... club intro go? 👀
Player: It went okay I think
Mabel: You're with your friend at least!
Mabel: How are the other members?
Player: Some interesting people in there 😅
Mabel: Really?
Mabel: Same here lol
Mabel: Actually, uhm.. random question
Mabel: Did they say you have to do anything?
- Like what?
	Player: Like what?
	Mabel: Yeah! Like I dunno, a task or so
	Mabel: Maybe like take pictures of yourself or something (totally random example!)
	Player: No lol
	Mabel: Really? Awh well that's it I guess
- No, do you?
	do echo_set([\"96\"])
	Player: No, do you?
	Mabel: Nope! Nothing 😅
	Mabel: Thought: Only THAT...
	Mabel: Thought: Hopefully I can quickly do that and never think about it again
	Mabel: Mhmm!
	Mabel: Totally a nothing burger see!
Player: If you say so
do echo_clear()
Player: Any plans for the weekend?
Mabel: Just doing some homework!
if Story.has_flag(\"Date3\"):
	Mabel: But I'm gonna see you tomorrow for our date 😊
	Player: Yep!
	Mabel: Excitinggg
	Mabel: Can't wait hehe
else:
	Mabel: Maybe I'll go shopping tomorrow too
	Mabel: Thought: I don't really have outfits like they want me to wear so I think I'll buy one
	Mabel: Not sure yet
Player: Okay! I'll let you finish up then
Mabel: Thanks babe!
Mabel: Talk soon?
Player: Yup 👍
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
